summary: Hey @taylorswift ! I'm Rodes (or Rose, if that's easier), I'm 19 and I'm from the Netherlands. I've been listening to your music...
body:
Hey @taylorswift ! I’m Rodes (or Rose, if that’s easier), I’m 19 and I’m from the Netherlands. I’ve been listening to your music since 2010and became a true Swiftie in 2011! It’s been 8 years and I have never seen you live but I plan on changing that soon!

Thank you for everything you do for me and my fellow Swifties. We love you forever ♡
